{"questionId":"25862","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Consider the vectors <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"bold-italic\">a</mi></math>&nbsp;and <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"bold-italic\">b</mi></math>&nbsp;such that&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"bold-italic\">a</mi><mo>=</mo><mfenced><mtable><mtr><mtd><mn>12</mn></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mo>-</mo><mn>5</mn></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced></math>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfenced open=\"|\" close=\"|\"><mi mathvariant=\"bold-italic\">b</mi></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mn>15</mn></math>.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>Find the possible range of values for&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfenced open=\"|\" close=\"|\"><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"bold-italic\">a</mi><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant=\"bold-italic\">b</mi></mrow></mfenced></math>.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfenced open=\"|\" close=\"|\"><mi mathvariant=\"bold-italic\">a</mi></mfenced><mo>=</mo><msqrt><msup><mn>12</mn><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mfenced><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>5</mn></mrow></mfenced><mn>2</mn></msup></msqrt><mfenced><mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>13</mn></mrow></mfenced></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>(A1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>2</mn><mo>≤</mo><mfenced open=\"|\" close=\"|\"><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"bold-italic\">a</mi><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant=\"bold-italic\">b</mi></mrow></mfenced><mo>≤</mo><mn>28</mn></math>&nbsp; (accept min <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>2</mn></math> and max <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>28</mn></math>)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Award <em><strong>(A1)A0</str